        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PERCEPTION_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Honkai Perception</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PERCEPTION_DESC" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Cost {1_Amount} [ICON_Faith] Honkai Energy[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]The beginning of everything. Allows the extraction of Honkai Energy veins and reveals basic Honkai phenomena.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_ST_FREYA_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>St. Freya Academy</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_ST_FREYA_DESC" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Cost {1_Amount} [ICON_Faith] Honkai Energy[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Unlocks the unique building [St. Freya Academy], allowing the training of novice Valkyries.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_SCHICKSAL_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Schicksal Armament</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_SCHICKSAL_DESC" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Cost {1_Amount} [ICON_Faith] Honkai Energy[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Unlocks unique Schicksal mechas and defensive tactics.</Text>
        </Row>
